Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside Advisor Suzuki's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Resides the Iron Tanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:09.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Designed by the master of traps, Samizu Kichiemon, in the final days of the Tokugawa shogunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's the strongest and most impregnable safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid sent a notice challenging the Iron Tanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its strong door had repelled many a thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he vowed to open it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the Iron Tanuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had been outfitted with an anti-theft security\Ndevice that relied on a motion sensor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which made it difficult to even approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing of the notice, Inspector Nakamori\Nassembled a massive police force, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite that, in the safe room that was equipped with the sensor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A second notice from Kid appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just how was he able to bypass the weight sensor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Kid has already infiltrated the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does he plan to open the door to the Iron Tanuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The unexpected contents of the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid finally shows his true face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kidâ€”have you found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:10.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Seto Mizuki (23)\NMaid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd probably be best if you didn't pass through this corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because they suspect you of being Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's all this brat's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's troubling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The master just ordered me to bring this food to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know since I just started, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As of late, it seems he's been taking his dinner alone in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the tableware is collected...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems there are always two plates missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not just the food and plates that are strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,After each meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:10.14,CharCard - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Akitsu Masuhiko (32)\NAssistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:10.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He always goes into the room to check on the safe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he does, it seems he never forgets to take along his cane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The uncle that is always full of such vigor does?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because plates and a cane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happen to be essential to opening the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the security device protecting the safe\Nreacts to the weight of a single cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't help much if the safe is really that easy to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm out of cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when the master called over on his extension...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any chance you could get some cigarettes for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when the master called over on his extension...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was wondering why dinner still hadn't been...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get right on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get my food to my room immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies for getting you so wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the maid or the assistant, both have proven worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one of any worth\Nis this bodyguard here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:45.86,CharCard - 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Gotou Zengo (38)\NBodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it you wanted earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That, once I was finished with dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should come "lend you a hand."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go to my room first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to turn off the security system!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though Kid could show up at any time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Checking the safe has become part of my daily routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this really be Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just two, three minutes will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And during that time, don't peek in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By saying that I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, would you mind keeping it down out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you may disturb the advisor while he's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always speaks to someone while inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's possible he's just talking to himself, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he forgot how to open the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And has to call someone for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor Suzuki has been having dinner\Nin his room lately, and eats it alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, afterward, two plates always disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as he checks the safe afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has reason to bring a cane...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And always talks to someone while he checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's also the peculiar notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said that dinner's ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, the check is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do as you please now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you go back to your room, your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with your bagâ€”do you mind if we check them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing of consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some old albums...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some writings and pictures from my childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sometimes take them back to my room to look over in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that there only seem to be albums here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope it won't be a problem if I go out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot that I promised to meet\Nup with Chaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Chaki!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are the car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get it ready on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure everything will be fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:09:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, that guy's natural enemy is here, in this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest is on you, little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an announcement to all those guarding the Suzuki residence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of Kaitou Kid's arrival could be any moment now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a precaution, neglect nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't think knowing someone's face is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The officer next to you could be Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy is a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he could be disguised as any of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as the brat said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the anti-theft device was first disabled earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those that could have placed the notice were...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bodyguard with the dark complexion, Gotou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mostly useless assistant, Akitsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the clumsy maid, Mizukiâ€”that's all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we don't have to worry about that bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just left with Uncle Jirokichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it must be either Akitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} or the maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's Akitsu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked him to fetch me some cigarettes, and haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the maid could have just been pretending, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspicious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, Uncle Jirokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Kid was acting as Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would already have the switch for turning off the security device...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And could put the notice there easily, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've mentioned that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the change fell out earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Uncle Jirokichi that picked one up and threw it to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what hand did he use then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was his right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when Uncle Jirokichi threw the car keys to the bodyguard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What hand did he use that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that true!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took it out of his coat pocket with his right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But specially changed it over to his left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And got it to the bodyguard that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's definitely strange, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean he's Kid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, shouldn't we hurry and tell Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we went after them now, we might be able to catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man might be Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can that be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor Suzuki just deactivated the security\Nsystem to get inside a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then went into the safe room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Checking the safe is part of his daily routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even had a body check performed on him and\Npersonally inspected the bag he brought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anything unusual in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old guy is on his way to meet up\Nwith Superintendent Chaki for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way that guy could be Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you mention me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Chaki!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you set to meet with Advisor Suzuki over dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I consent to something so easy-going at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhmâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to collect the tableware from the master's room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door was slightly open and, when I looked in the closet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The master tied up inside, sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the old man who just left was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just there to confirm it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are countless wires stretched over the closet and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a sign that reads, "Danger, do not touch" attached...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means it won't be easy to get our hands on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:12:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When that old guy went in earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was only for two or three minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I've already seen that which lies inside\Nthe stomach of the Iron Tanuki," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His objective from the beginning was to just open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he's already met his goal then, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's better if you don't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Kid was the one with the switch, he probably left it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want Team A cooperating with the bomb\Nsquad to rescue Advisor Suzuki immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the rest of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chase after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems we have a bit of commotion behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it and just lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that it's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Means it's all going as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a minute ago, there were so many riot squad members here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:24.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\xbord5\ybord3}Quote from Oku no Hosomichi, a haibun work by Matsuo Bashou
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"All that remains of brave soldiers' dreams," I'd imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems they're still trying to rescue Uncle in his room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} was actually Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should have been more friendly around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that's true, isn't something strange about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the device was first switched off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Jirokichi who put the notice there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must've been Kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the Jirokichi who picked up the change was the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then the Jirokichi that tossed the car keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Kid again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So only the first instance and the last instance\Nwere Kid, with the real one in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was the switch made?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, wasn't Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} acting strange as... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has he already disappeared again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, our opposition here is the "Magician\NUnder the Moonlight," Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brat has probably moved onto something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After we find that brat, we're heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a disappointment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must love it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disguising as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just so much more cute this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he said to hurry and bring his food...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:16:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You resumed the role of the clumsy maid and hurried\Nover, hitting Uncle with the dining cart in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you didn't expect Uncle to drop his wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And scatter around coins in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't about to be careless by\Npicking them up and leaving fingerprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you only had your bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That said, it would have also been\Nunnatural to stand there and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you spilled the water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the change had become wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would no longer be strange to wipe them down\Nwith a handkerchief as you collected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You discovered I was Kid just from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real telling moment was when you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That, once I was finished with dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should come "lend you a hand."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when it all unraveled...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mystery behind the dated writing in the first notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you take the final letters of each line starting from the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It reads, "Lend me a hand."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first notice was written by the advisor himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a request for aid from him to Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he heard you say that, he realized who you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And took you to his room to plan how to get rid of the riot squad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tossing of the key with his left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the lie about having the dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the placing of the card on the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all to make everyone think Kid was the advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the one tied up in the closet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably Akitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who you disguised as the advisor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That looks complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Need my help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that door back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a number of indentations, as if something had hit it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That probably means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this dial isn't turned just right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, leave it to a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This tile over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it oddly new?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A truly great safe by the master of traps, Kichiemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:54.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\xbord3\ybord3}You Lose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy's really too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you already know why I was called here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did help by having the police fall\Ninto the plan and chase him, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only because of Advisor Suzuki's strange behavior lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had been having dinner alone in his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to get fresh water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason two plates would disappear each time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because one was to hold the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the other carried the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, those two plates were fed under the door of the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By using his cane to push them inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was always talking while inside, and saying\Nsomething like, "Hold on just a bit longer," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All for the one swallowed by the Iron Tanuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the old guy said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be on the underside of the bandanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guide to opening the Iron Tanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had to use this to open it every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that was why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only realized after the door was closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That his dog Lupin wasn't with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he had to come to me crying for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the only one who can open such\Na masterful safe in such short time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be the one and only Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I already told you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I'm the real Suzuki Jirokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Chaki said you never scheduled a dinner with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not Chaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one I was to meet was an old friend by the name of Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means Kid is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've already discovered that old guy\Nwas the real deal and are on their way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this is a real risk, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This could have all been a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I considered that at first too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After visiting in secret and seeing the reason, I decided to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm a big fan of the real "gentleman thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To see Lupin completely shut away in that dark cage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just stand by, could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try to get too friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, don't you get too friendly either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By name, we're meant to be enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lupin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was trapped in the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he had to ask Kid to open it for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a secret from society, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, he didn't give Kid anything for helping, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that would have to wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until there are handcuffs around both of his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.15,0:23:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
